summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2008 PACE AMERICAN WORK SPORT TRAILER. THE CONTACT STATED THAT THERE WERE SHARP EDGES ON THE CROSS MEMBERS OF THE TRAILER WHERE SOMEONE COULD POSSIBLY CUT THEMSELVES IF WORKING ON THE TRAILER. THE MANUFACTURER WAS CONTACTED BUT HAD NOT OFFERED ANY ASSISTANCE. NO REPAIRS WERE PERFORMED TO THE VEHICLE.  THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 800. THE VIN WAS UNAVAILABLE.
